                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-2"></div>
                            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10">
                                <div class="btn">
                                    <span id="suggest_save">提交</span>
                                    <!-- <input type="submit" name="" value="提交"/> -->
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
        		</div>
        		<div class="tips well top10">
        			<div>注意事项：</div>
        				<p>1. 请勿提交任何涉及政治、暴力、色情等违法信息；恶意提交不法信息者，将被封号！<br>
